turns out that Wells has written a number of books about about
Ile-Rein at various points during its history.  &lt;cite&gt;The Element of
Fire&lt;/cite&gt; is set during Ile-Rein's era of muskets and swords, and is a
very good mixture of swashbuckling and magic.  I look forward to
reading more of Wells' works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
